```typescript
export declare const wrapHandlerToThrowResponses: <T extends RequestInfo = RequestInfo>(
  handler: RouteFunction<T> | RouteComponent<T>
) => RouteHandler<T>;
```

Wraps a handler that might return a `Response` so that the response is thrown to break out of React rendering context.

